me.taylorkelly.mywarp.service.teleport

Class EconomyTeleportService

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.common.collect.ForwardingObject
      • me.taylorkelly.mywarp.service.teleport.EconomyTeleportService
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TeleportService

    public class EconomyTeleportService
extends com.google.common.collect.ForwardingObject
    Bills users for teleporting and cancels the teleport if the entity cannot afford it.

    Only LocalPlayers are billed, other entitys are simply teleported. The teleport itself is delegated to another TeleportService.
